In this PR, we give constructors for Mayer-Vietoris squares, which allows the construction of these squares in the case of topological spaces.

---

- [x] depends on: #14957
- [x] depends on: #14951
- [x] depends on: #14890
- [x] depends on: #14935 
- [x] depends on: #14936
